{"type":null,"faqId":16540,"title":"How do I update my Talkband B1's firmware and app versions?","answer":"Your B1 supports OTA updates. To update your B1's firmwareand app, perform the following steps:<br>\n<br>\n1. Ensure that your B1 is connected to your phoneproperly over Bluetooth.<br>\n<br>\n2.&nbsp;Run <strong>Huawei TalkBand</strong> on your phone and choose <strong>Settings</strong>&gt;<strong>About</strong>.<br>\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141120053543667001.png\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141120053551729001.png\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141120053556513001.png\"><br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n3.&nbsp;Touch <strong>Update TalkBand</strong> to update your B1'sfirmware.<br>\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141120053623384001.png\"><br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n4.&nbsp;Touch <strong>Update TalkBand</strong> app to update your Huawei TalkBand app.<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;<br>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":10,"unUseful":3,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"9140","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1416433111000,"seriesProductName":"B1","visitedTimes":771,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"Talkband B1,software update,firmware,app version","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}